#

Beetroot Soup

45 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

HealthySoupVegetarian

Description

A vibrant and nourishing beetroot soup that's both earthy and sweet, perfect for a light yet satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • beetroot: 4 medium, peeled and chopped
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • carrot: 1 large, peeled and chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • potatoes: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: for garnish
